  <data name="Winget_Description" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Isoftware yokuchaza izithombe zesikrini ye-Windows ne-Linux.

Izici:
- **Imicibisholo** - Nxenxa ukunakwa ezindaweni ezithile ngemicibisholo enguqukayo
- **Izithangami** - Engeza izichazelo ze-bubble enekheli elingashintshwa
- **Amanothi** - Dala izibhokisi zombhalo ezinolwazi olwengeziwe
- **Ukugqamisa umngcele** - Gqamisa izindawo ngezibhokisi ezinemingcele
- **Ukufingqa** - Fihla ulwazi oluyimfihlo ngezinto zokufingqa
- **Ithuluzi lokukhethwa** - Khetha izingxenye zesithombe ukuze ukopisha (Ctrl+C) noma ususe (ukhiye we-Delete)
- **Ukusika ngokuphezulu nangezansi** - Sika izindawo ezisuka ngokuphezulu noma ngezansi zesithombe
- **Ukugqamisa** - Gqamisa izindawo ezinomdlandla
- **Ukuphathwa kwamaphrojekthi** - Ukulondoloza iphrojekthi ngokuzenzakalelayo nezithombe ezincane zokuphana
- **Izinhlelo** - Isebenza ku-Windows naku-Linux</value>
  </data>
